# Expense Tracker App

An interactive web app built with **Python** and **Streamlit** to help users analyze their monthly income, expenses, and savings. This project was developed as part of a hands-on assignment to apply financial logic, data visualization, and user interaction in a real-world context.

---

## Features

-  Input monthly income and expenses
-  Calculate savings and savings percentage
-  Set and compare savings goals
-  Break down expenses into Essentials, Wants, and Investments
-  Visualize financial health with dynamic feedback
-  Session state to retain data during interaction

---

##Tech Stack

| Tool       | Purpose                          |
|------------|----------------------------------|
| Python     | Core programming language        |
| Streamlit  | Web app framework                |
| Pandas     | Data handling and calculations   |
| Git & GitHub | Version control and deployment |

